title: Yoli BBR New Years Kick Off Event Hosted by YNA
desc: We invite you to join us on January 9th, 2016 for our annual Yoli BBR (Better Body Resolution) January kick off event hosted by Yoli Nation Acamdy (YNA) to help usher in the brand new year! This is a great opportunity for those looking to JUMP START their 2016 year on the right foot with YOLI. This event is OPEN to ALL YOLI members and Preffered Customers (PCs). Our morning "AM" session will be jam packed with amazing PRODUCT and HEALTH focused content and our "PM" session will be jam packed with BUSINESS content! Come learn from some of the BEST in YOLI! Surprised guests TO BE ANNOUNCED! We will also be raffling away some AMAZING PRIZES! Let's make 2016 YOUR YEAR! Date: January 9, 2016 Time: 9am - 3pm (8am registration) Location: Orange County Business Expo Center 1960 S. Anaheim Way, Anaheim,CA 92805 Food: Food trucks for easy lunch options will be available
